window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A brilliantly imaginative and poignant fairy tale from the modern master of wonder and terror, <em>The Ocean at the End of the Lane</em> is Neil Gaiman’s first new novel for adults since his #1 <em>New York Times</em> bestseller <em>Anansi Boys.</em></p><p>This bewitching and harrowing tale of mystery and survival, and memory and magic, makes the impossible all too real...</p>"; 
